<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.5.1">
<l>vaḷavē ḻulakiṉ mutalāy vāṉō riṟaiyai yaruviṉaiyēṉ</l>
<l>kaḷavēḻ veṇṇey toṭuvuṇṭa kaḷvā veṉpaṉ piṉṉaiyun</l>
<l>taḷavēḻ muṟuval piṉṉaikkāy vallā ṉāyar talaivaṉā</l>
<l>yiḷavē ṟēḻun taḻuviya ventā yeṉpa ṉiṉaintunaintē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To the lord of the celestials, being the cause of the fertile seven worlds, I of difficult karma</l>
<l>say “o robber who touched [and] ate the butter lifted  by theft”, and after</l>
<l>thinking, I faintly say “my father who embraced the seven young bulls</l>
<l>as the leader of the herders of strong cows for the sake of Piṉṉai in whose smile jasmine-[bud-like teeth] rise.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
